commit.title: [genarg] Remove some deprecated genargs.
commit.message:
[genarg] Remove some deprecated genargs.

No point on having these aliases; note that there are issues with the
current setup for `wit_preident/wit_pre_ident` and `wit_ref`.

[`ref` is taken as the keyword for example, the entry for preident
doesn't match the alias]
